# Lyris

Lyris is an AI-powered chatbot focused on music and poetry. It helps users with lyric writing, poetry creation, creative ideation, and expressive conversation.

## Features
- Music-focused chatbot support
- Poetry assistance
- Lyric generation and refinement
- Creative brainstorming
- Future audio and music tool integration

